es of India |title=Bihar is country's fastest growing state at 13.1% |date=2 June 2012 |ref={{sfnRef|''The Times of India''|2 June 2012}}}}\n* {{cite news |url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/politics/nation/contrary-to-modis-projections-gujarats-growth-story-is-riddled-with-contradictions/articleshow/14048496.cms |work=The Times of India |title=Contrary to Modi's projections, Gujarat's growth story is riddled with contradictions&nbsp;\u2013 The Economic Times |date=12 June 2012 |ref={{sfnRef|''The Economic Times''|12 June 2012}} | first1=Bhalchandra | last1=Mungekar}}\n* {{cite news |url=http://www.thehindubusinessline.com/2005/10/07/stories/2005100702790400.htm |title=Flextronics signs pact for Chennai facility |work=The Hindu Business Line |date=7 October 2005 |accessdate=10 September 2012 |ref={{sfnRef|''Business Line''|7 October 2005}} |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100902122159/http://www.thehindubusinessline.com/2005/10/07/stories/2005100702790400.htm |archivedate=2 September 2010  }}\n* {{cite news |url=http://www.thehindubusinessline.com/2006/05/07/stories/2006050702500300.htm |title=TN software exports clock 32 pc growth |work=The Hindu Business Line |date=7 May 2006 |accessdate=10 September 2012 |ref={{sfnRef|''Business Line''|7 May 2006}} |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091008003307/http://www.thehindubusinessline.com/2006/05/07/stories/2006050702500300.htm |archivedate=8 October 2009  }}\n* {{cite news |url=http://www.financialexpress.com/news/tn-makes-its-way-to-top-5-states-in-hdi/287643/ |title=TN makes its way to top 5 states in HDI |date=24 March 2008 |accessdate=24 March 2008 |ref={{sfnRef|''The Financial Express''|24 March 2008}}}}\n* {{cite news |url=http://www.hindu.com/2008/05/18/stories/2008051853960400.htm |title=Tamil Nadu the most urbanised State: Minister |work=The Hindu |date=18 May 2008 |accessdate=10 September 2012 |ref={{sfnRef|''The Hindu''|18 May 2008}} |location=Chenna