embly.tn.gov.in/history/history.htm |title=Tamil Nadu Legislative Assembly history |publisher=Assembly.tn.gov.in |year=2012 |accessdate=10 September 2012 |ref={{sfnRef|Tamil Nadu Legislative Assembly history|2012}} |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100413233934/http://www.assembly.tn.gov.in/history/history.htm |archivedate=13 April 2010  }}\n* {{cite web |work=16th if Union Territories are included |url=http://wcd.nic.in/publication/GDIGEReport/Part2.pdf |title=HDI and GDI Estimates for India and the States/UTs: Results and Analysis |accessdate=4 July 2012 |publisher=GDIGE |ref={{sfnRef|HDI and GDI estimates|2012}} |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120316160655/http://wcd.nic.in/publication/GDIGEReport/Part2.pdf |archivedate=16 March 2012  }}\n* {{cite web |url=http://socialjustice.nic.in/pdf/tab16.pdf |title=Human Development Index of India & Major States, 1981&nbsp;\u2013 2001 |publisher=Union Ministry of Social Justice |year=2001 |accessdate=4 July 2012 |ref={{sfnRef|Human Development Index|2001}} |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130722093933/http://socialjustice.nic.in/pdf/tab16.pdf |archivedate=22 July 2013  }}\n* {{cite web |url=http://mospi.nic.in/mospi_new/upload/census_2012/EC_main_2012.htm |title=Sixth Economic Census |publisher=Ministry of Statistics and Programme Implementation, Gov of India |year=2012 |accessdate=10 September 2012 |ref={{sfnRef|Sixth Economic Census}} |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121113225608/http://www.mospi.nic.in/mospi_new/upload/census_2012/EC_main_2012.htm |archivedate=13 November 2012  }}\n* {{cite web |url=http://pib.nic.in/release/release.asp?relid=29977 |title=Press Information Bureau English Releases |publisher=Pib.nic.in |year=2012 |accessdate=10 September 2012 |ref={{sfnRef|Press Information Bureau releases|2012}}}}\n* {{cite web |url=https://whc.unesco.org/en/list |title=UNESCO World Heritage List |publisher=Whc.unesco.