andookaan''\n |Desi Beam ft. Bohemia\n |Desi Beam\n |-\n |2011\n |''Bulawa''\n |Bohemia ft. [[Pakman]] & D-Naar,\n |Bohemia\n |-\n |2011\n |''Jee Karda''\n |Bobby B ft. Bohemia,\n |Bobby B\n |-\n |2012\n |''Chadd Ditta''\n |Bohemia ft. Mixman Shawn\n |Bohemia\n |-\n |2012\n |''Maar Charapa''\n |Sir Punj ft. Bohemia\n |Sir Punj & [[Rishi Rich]]  (Unreleased Track)\n |- \n |2012\n |''Adhi Raat''\n |[[Jasmine Sandlas]] ft. Bohemia\n |Bohemia\n |-\n |2012\n |''Jaane Jana'' \n |J.Hind ft. Bohemia\n |J.Hind\n |- \n |2012\n |''Paigam''\n |Bohemia\n |Bohemia\n |-\n |2012\n |''Talli ''\n |Gitta Bains ft. Bohemia\n |Tigerstyle\n |-\n |2013\n |''Rooh (the Soul)''\n |Bohemia\n |Bohemia\n |- \n |2013\n |''Rooh'' Remix\n |Bohemia ft. Pardhaan\n |Bohemia\n |-\n |2013\n |''My Ride Remix''\n |The Bilz & Kashif ft. [[Glasses Malone]], Bohemia, Drega, Nivla \n |-\n |2014\n |''Phenomenon''\n |Bohemia\n |Bohemia\n |-\n |2014\n |''Bad Boy''\n |D Major  ft. Bohemia\n |Tigerstyle\n |-\n |2014\n |''Brand New Swag''\n |Bohemia ft. Haji Springer & Panda\n |Bohemia\n |-\n |2014\n |''Yaad Anah''\n |Bohemia\n |Bohemia\n |-\n |2014\n |''Preet''\n |Haji Springer ft. Pree Mayall & Bohemia\n |Haji Springer\n |-\n |2014\n |''U n Me''\n |[[Sean Kingston]] ft. [[Sonu Kakkar]], & Bohemia\n |[[Iraj Weeraratne|Iraj]]\n |-\n |2014\n |''Akkha Mumbai''\n |Mun E. Fame ft. Bohemia\n |Mun E. Fame\n |-\n |2014\n |''Fire''\n |Gitta Bains ft. Bohemia\n |Haji Springer\n |-\n |2014\n |''Saheli''\n |Gurdeep Mehndi ft. Bohemia\n |Gurdeep Mehndi\n |-\n |2014\n |''Wake N Bake ''\n |Bohemia ft. Avenue OB\n |Avenue OB\n |-\n |2014\n |''Main''\n |Bohemia\n |Bohemia\n |-\n |2014\n |''Meri Bandook''\n |Haji Springer ft. Bohemia\n |Haji Springer\n |-\n |2015\n |''Devil inside''\n |Haji Springer ft. Bohemia\n |Haji Springer\n |-\n |2015 \n |''Koi Ni Parwaa'' \n |Haji Springer ft. Bohemia\n |Haji Springer\n |-\n |2015\n |''Jaguar''\n |[[Sukh-E]] ft. Bohemia\n |[[Sukh-E]]\n |-\n |2015\n |''Tension Stress'' (Bengali)\n |Master-D 